Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.40,0:24:25.44,Cartello BASE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs30\b0\c&HFDFDFD&\fnArial\1a&H4A&\pos(192.69,91.038)}Anteprima
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:06.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma questo è... odore di benzina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.99,0:24:11.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Perché proprio Kogoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.92,0:24:13.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,C'entra la nave fantasma?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.27,0:24:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nessun detective che si rispetti\N fuggirebbe di fronte al pericolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.68,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Perché ce l'hai con me?!
